_header: Then had Herod received the crown
_description: Gospel, In festo sanctorum Innocentium, in the ‘expanded’ Northern Homily Cycle

BLHar4196.First Lines: Þan had herod resayued þe crowneWith realte & with grete renowne…
BLHar4196.Last Lines: …Twa hundreth stades was þe spaceffra þare he died vnto þat place
BLHar4196.Note: Preceded by Latin, “Angelus domini aperuit & cetera.”
BLHar4196.Attributed Title: Sanctorum innocencium martyrum Euangelium secundum Matheum (rubric, f. 24rb)
